## Artifact Persistence Protocol

**Rule**: Never rely solely on context window. Write to disk.

```
_migration_memory/
├── TERRITORY_MAP.md           # Directory structure
├── canvas_implementation.md   # What works in canvas
├── domain_knowledge.md        # ECM, RAMS, formulas
├── math_and_solver.md         # Algorithms, constraints
├── competitors.md             # SignatureRail, Railnova
├── patternfly_mapping.md      # Component decisions
├── decision_history.md        # From git
└── SYNTHESIS_NOTES.md         # Cross-cutting findings
```

